text: Michael Naray is an archer from Australia. Naray competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics.Michael NARAY He was born on 3 August 1970.Michael Naray Naray is now a science teacher at a school in Sydney, Australia as of 23 April 2025. == References == Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Australian archers Category:Olympians for Australia
